1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
A scheme.

2
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,129
He is not the Medicine King.

3
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,920
Did I make a mistake?

4
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:15,120
Father!

5
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,320
You are so vicious.

6
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:23,800
You actually used dark magic to openly harm my father.

7
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:25,600
All of this

8
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:28,000
was indeed your doing.

9
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,920
Consort De's father was not in the Book of Life and Death,

10
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,720
yet he also died a violent death.

11
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,840
It was clearly Liuchuan.

12
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,560
He just

13
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:35,800
secretly attacked.

14
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,640
What reason does he have to do this?

15
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:40,240
Because he is a remnant of the Yaoshen Society.

16
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:44,920
Reporting to the Empress Dowager,

17
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,800
I can prove

18
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,960
who the mastermind behind all this is.

19
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:48,640
It's him.

20
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:53,580
As everyone knows,

21
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,320
I destroyed the Yaoshen Society back then,

22
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,840
so I know all about this.

23
00:01:57,280 --> 00:02:00,120
And these things were brought into the palace by him.

24
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,520
Ever since he entered the palace,

25
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:04,040
the Book of Life and Death murder case occurred.

26
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,560
Prince Jia, perhaps you have forgotten.

27
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:08,520
You were the one who invited Liu Chuan into the palace.

28
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,039
I was foolish at the time.

29
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,520
I thought he had the same intelligence as Brother Zhuoran.

30
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,440
I didn't expect him to exhaust all schemes

31
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,640
just to enter the palace.

32
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,520
He pretended to eradicate the Medicine God Society,

33
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,380
but in reality,

34
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,920
he was seeking revenge for them.

35
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:22,610
Besides,

36
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,640
he is not Liu Chuan at all.

37
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,400
Your Highness,

38
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,840
what you're saying is too absurd.

39
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,400
Absurd?

40
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,450
Haven't you noticed

41
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,920
that Liu Chuan is different from before?

42
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,520
Because the real Liu Chuan

43
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,320
is already dead.

44
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:38,760
Guards!

45
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,360
Bring the man up.

46
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,000
Who exactly are you?

47
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,340
Prince Jia, you...

48
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,720
You impersonated Liu Chuan to carry out a poisonous scheme.

49
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,280
What else do you have to say?

50
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,920
Such an evil person must be beheaded

51
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:10,130
to settle this matter and restore peace to the harem.

52
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,440
Empress Dowager.

53
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:14,560
Please allow me to verify the facts before taking action.

54
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,820
Yes, Empress Dowager.

55
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:16,520
About this matter,

56
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,480
there must be more to it.

57
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,680
Then how do you explain Liu Chuan's corpse?

58
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,920
Commoners' bones are left exposed.

59
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,579
How dare you, monster,

60
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:26,079
cause trouble in the palace!

61
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,880
Throw him into the dungeon!

62
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,760
If you dare to move,

63
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:32,250
I will have him executed immediately.

64
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,920
You are out of tricks this time, aren't you?

65
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,280
The first time I saw you,

66
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,560
I knew you were no good.

67
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,100
But you won't get your way either.

68
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,280
You didn't get the antidote.

69
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,520
I am in no rush.

70
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,690
I have plenty of antidotes.

71
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,120
Men!

72
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:01,600
Take him away.

73
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,920
Father.

74
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,120
Father.

75
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,600
Brother Liu,

76
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:51,520
you must be starving.

77
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,760
But there's no other way.

78
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,520
If you were full,

79
00:04:58,159 --> 00:05:00,760
I'm afraid even this prison couldn't hold you.

80
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:03,720
Seems you've investigated me thoroughly.

81
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,320
Do you have a crush on me?

82
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,060
Your Highness.

83
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,080
Liu Chuan is dead.

84
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,600
Now there is someone identical in appearance

85
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,000
acting under his name,

86
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,320
behaving strangely,

87
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:20,290
similar to the ways of Prince Zhuoran.

88
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,920
I really appreciate your talent,

89
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,680
but there is no way you can work for me.

90
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,960
How foolish.

91
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,330
I think you're the foolish one.

92
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,560
How so?

93
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:48,250
You thought you hid yourself well,

94
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,600
but as I expected,

95
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,380
you exposed yourself.

96
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,720
So what?

97
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,480
Aren't you still in prison?

98
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,160
I just didn't expect

99
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:03,760
that to frame me,

100
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,660
you killed so many people.

101
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,570
I will get justice sooner or later.

102
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,320
Such arrogance.

103
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,160
Justice?

104
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:16,080
Someone is coming to get justice from you right now.

105
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,120
Jianqin?

106
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,400
He...

107
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,280
killed your master

108
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:54,340
and impersonated Liu Chuan, playing you all for fools.

109
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:58,000
I am giving you a chance for revenge now.

110
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,600
Kill him.

111
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:09,200
You are really not the Young Master.

112
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:11,600
Jianqin,

113
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:12,840
I'm sorry.

114
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:13,920
Say no more.

115
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,320
No matter what,

116
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,560
for killing the Young Master,

117
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,960
I will never forgive you.

118
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,320
I didn't mean to deceive you.

119
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,200
I wanted to help your Young Master

120
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,260
find out the truth.

121
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,050
I don't care.

122
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,400
As long as he is good to me,

123
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,600
he is my Young Master.

124
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,159
You killed the real Liu Chuan.

125
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,159
So what?

126
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,120
He's just

127
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:52,120
one of my many drug testings.

128
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:54,000
He should be grateful.

129
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,680
You killed the young master.

130
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,640
I'll kill you.

131
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:57,960
Jianqin.

132
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,800
If you had worked for me earlier,

133
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,760
maybe these people wouldn't have died.

134
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,800
You did all this

135
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,800
just for the antidote.

136
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:17,450
When I wiped out the God of Medicine Association,

137
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,800
I was quite interested in the Skull Grass.

138
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,860
I just didn't expect it to be so toxic.

139
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,480
I developed many new drugs,

140
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,810
but none of them worked.

141
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,650
The poisoned people still die.

142
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,520
But I am merciful

143
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,330
and don't like to take people's lives.

144
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,220
You make it sound nice.

145
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,320
Rather than taking people's lives,

146
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,720
what you really want to do

147
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,120
is show your cruelty and viciousness.

148
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,120
That's right.

149
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,210
If I can control these poisoned people

150
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:46,320
so they won't die from sores,

151
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:50,000
wouldn't the world be at my fingertips?

152
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,610
Where is the new prescription?

153
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,760
So you set a trap for me,

154
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,840
and used so many people's lives

155
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,600
to force me to hand over the antidote.

156
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,760
If back then at the Imperial Medical Bureau,

157
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:02,690
you had given me the prescription,

158
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,650
everything would have fallen into place.

159
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:09,180
I didn't expect you to bring this upon yourself.

160
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,780
So where is the prescription now?

161
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,120
I believe

162
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,800
you must have developed it.

163
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,800
Are you crazy?

164
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,080
Things have gotten to this point.

165
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,080
Even if I had it, I wouldn't tell you.

166
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,450
At least negotiate some terms.

167
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,160
Is this it?

168
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,920
And you call yourself a Prince?

169
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:33,960
Terms?

170
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,080
You want to negotiate terms with me?

171
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,080
Are these terms good enough?

172
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,340
The antidote has already been verified.

173
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,600
It really works.

174
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,680
I was not wrong about you.

175
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,880
I knew you wouldn't let me go.

176
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,120
Can my life

177
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,480
plus the antidote

178
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,260
be exchanged for their lives?

179
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,330
You won't lose out on this deal.

180
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:01,720
No.

181
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,720
Only if I die,

182
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,680
can he complete his plan in peace.

183
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:11,760
Master, don't.

184
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:12,760
Young Master Liu.

185
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,320
You still have a long life ahead.

186
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,080
Live well.

187
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,480
Master.

188
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,160
Liu Chuan, don't.

189
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:28,080
Liuchuan, no!

190
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:37,320
I used the strongest Skull Grass.

191
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:40,160
You shouldn't be able to survive this time.

192
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:41,800
Liuchuan,

193
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:44,340
you haven't told me about that novel yet.

194
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,080
Prince Jia.

195
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,600
Prince Jia, you killed me!

196
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,120
Young Master.

197
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,480
Liuchuan.

198
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,360
Mr. Liu,

199
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,840
thank you.

200
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:11,160
Young Master.

201
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:14,040
Otherwise, how can we explain this to the Master and Madam?

202
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:14,880
Don't do that.

203
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:16,410
Give me the reward quickly.

204
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:17,880
Young Master,

205
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:18,880
don't run away.

206
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,480
I will be yours sooner or later.

207
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:40,360
Liu Chuan.

208
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,760
Brother Wang.

209
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,640
Liu Chuan is dead.

210
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,120
But in my heart,

211
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,450
I have long regarded him as my husband.

212
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,400
If it weren't for them,

213
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,580
how could Liu Chuan have failed my affection

214
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,520
and ended up like this?

215
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,680
I will use their lives

216
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,680
to pay tribute to my husband.

217
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,640
Liuchuan.

218
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,320
Young Master.

219
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:09,880
Liuchuan,

220
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,840
wake up.

221
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,320
Master Liu.
